### AgentBin A2A Test File
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### Toggle @baseUrl between local and Azure as needed.

@baseUrl = https://agentbin.greensmoke-1163cb63.eastus.azurecontainerapps.io
# @baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### HEALTH CHECK
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AGENT CARDS — v1.0
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Echo Agent Card (v1.0)
GET {{baseUrl}}/echo/.well-known/agent-card.json
A2A-Version: 1.0

### Spec Agent Card (v1.0)
GET {{baseUrl}}/spec/.well-known/agent-card.json
A2A-Version: 1.0

### Root listing (v1.0)
GET {{baseUrl}}/.well-known/agent-card.json
A2A-Version: 1.0

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### AGENT CARDS — v0.3 (no A2A-Version header)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Echo Agent Card (v0.3 — has protocolVersion, url at top level)
GET {{baseUrl}}/echo/.well-known/agent-card.json

### Spec Agent Card (v0.3)
GET {{baseUrl}}/spec/.well-known/agent-card.json

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### v1.0 — ECHO AGENT
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Echo — simple message (v1.0)
POST {{baseUrl}}/echo
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "echo-v10-1",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-echo-v10-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "Hello from v1.0 client!" }]
    }
  }
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### v1.0 — SPEC AGENT: message-only
### Returns a message response (no task created)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Message Only (v1.0)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "msg-only-v10",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-mo-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "message-only hello world" }]
    }
  }
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### v1.0 — SPEC AGENT: task-lifecycle
### Full task state machine: submitted → working → completed
### Returns a task with artifacts
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Task Lifecycle (v1.0)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "task-lc-v10",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-lc-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "task-lifecycle process this data" }]
    }
  }
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### v1.0 — SPEC AGENT: task-failure
### Task transitions to failed state with error message
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Task Failure (v1.0)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "task-fail-v10",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-fail-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "task-failure trigger error" }]
    }
  }
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### v1.0 — SPEC AGENT: task-cancel
### Step 1: Start a cancellable task (stays in working state)
### Step 2: Cancel it with CancelTask using the returned taskId
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Task Cancel — Step 1: Start task
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "task-cancel-start",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-cancel-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "task-cancel start" }]
    }
  }
}

### Task Cancel — Step 2: Cancel it (replace TASK_ID_HERE with id from above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "CancelTask",
  "id": "task-cancel-do",
  "params": {
    "id": "TASK_ID_HERE"
  }
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### v1.0 — SPEC AGENT: multi-turn
### Step 1: Start conversation (returns input-required state)
### Step 2: Continue with task reference (say "done" to complete)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Multi-Turn — Step 1: Start
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "mt-start",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-mt-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "multi-turn start conversation" }]
    }
  }
}

### Multi-Turn — Step 2: Reply (replace TASK_ID_HERE with id from above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "mt-reply",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-mt-2",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "here is more input" }]
    },
    "taskId": "TASK_ID_HERE"
  }
}

### Multi-Turn — Step 3: Complete (replace TASK_ID_HERE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "mt-done",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-mt-3",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "done" }]
    },
    "taskId": "TASK_ID_HERE"
  }
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### v1.0 — SPEC AGENT: streaming
### SSE response with status updates and artifact chunks
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Streaming (v1.0)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendStreamingMessage",
  "id": "stream-v10",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-stream-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "streaming generate output" }]
    }
  }
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### v1.0 — SPEC AGENT: long-running
### Returns a working task — poll with GetTask to watch progress
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Long Running — Start (v1.0)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "SendMessage",
  "id": "long-start",
  "params": {
    "message": {
      "messageId": "msg-long-1",
      "role": "ROLE_USER",
      "parts": [{ "text": "long-running start process" }]
    }
  }
}

### Long Running — Poll (replace TASK_ID_HERE with id from above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json
A2A-Version: 1.0

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "GetTask",
  "id": "long-poll",
  "params": {
    "id": "TASK_ID_HERE"
  }
}

