### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### v0.3 — GetTask / CancelTask
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get Task (v0.3 — replace TASK_ID_HERE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "tasks/get",
  "id": "get-v03",
  "params": {
    "id": "TASK_ID_HERE"
  }
}

### Cancel Task (v0.3 — replace TASK_ID_HERE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/spec
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "tasks/cancel",
  "id": "cancel-v03",
  "params": {
    "id": "TASK_ID_HERE"
  }
}
